sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Browser
    participant React as React Frontend
    participant Axios
    participant Router as Django URL Router
    participant TM as TenantMiddleware
    participant Perm as DRF Permission Check
    participant View
    participant Svc as Service
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Browser->>React: User action (click / form submit)
    React->>Axios: api.get / api.post(url, data)
    Axios->>Router: HTTP request<br/>Cookie: sessionid=…<br/>Header: X-CSRFToken=…

    Router->>TM: Route matched — pass request through middleware
    TM->>TM: Read session → look up Practitioner<br/>Attach request.tenant (FK on user)
    TM->>Perm: Forward request with tenant set

    Perm->>Perm: IsAuthenticated → check session<br/>HasPermission("Module:Action")<br/>→ query user_roles + role_permissions
    alt Permission denied
        Perm-->>Axios: 403 Forbidden (JSON)
        Axios-->>React: Promise.reject(err)
        React-->>Browser: Inline error Alert shown
    else Permission granted
        Perm->>View: call view method
        View->>Svc: service.get_patients(request)
        Svc->>Repo: repo.get_all_for_tenant(tenant_id)
        Repo->>DB: SELECT … WHERE tenant_id = %s
        DB-->>Repo: Result rows
        Repo-->>Svc: QuerySet / ORM objects
        Svc-->>View: Processed / filtered data
        View-->>Axios: DRF Response (serialised JSON, 200 OK)
        Axios-->>React: Promise.resolve(response)
        React-->>Browser: Re-render with new data
    end
